Package ji.common.structures

Class DictionaryValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • ji.common.structures.DictionaryValue
  • public class DictionaryValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Class is wrapper for any object. The class is able to convert some common types to another or parse from one type to another. For example can parse numbers or times from string
